  <entry>
    <title>AWS EKS PV 设定</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/02/04/eks-pv/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/02/04/eks-pv/</id>
    <published>2021-02-04T06:18:48.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-02-04T13:49:53.030Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在进行操作前依据以下文档安装EBS CSI driver<br>依照中文版说明安装<br><a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/zh_cn/eks/latest/userguide/ebs-csi.html">EBS CSI driver doc </a></p><p>安装csi driver 后<br><img src="https://webnote.s3.cn-northwest-1.amazonaws.com.cn/20210204-csi.png" alt="csi"></p><p>Storage Class - 管理员提供了一种描述他们提供的存储的“类”的方法。 不同的类可能映射到服务质量级别，或备份策略，或者由群集管理员确定的任意策略</p><p>storage class 范例</p><p><strong>需要注意在type 部份注明EBS type 否则可能创建出 gp3等type</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kind: StorageClass</span><br><span class="line">apiVersion: storage.k8s.io&#x2F;v1</span><br><span class="line">metadata:</span><br><span class="line">  name: ebs-sc</span><br><span class="line">parameters:</span><br><span class="line">  fsType: ext4</span><br><span class="line">  type: gp2</span><br><span class="line">provisioner: ebs.csi.aws.com</span><br><span class="line">volumeBindingMode: WaitForFirstConsumer</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>PVC - Persistent Volume Claim 是用户实际的存储的请求<br>PVC 范例<br>在PNC 中指定access mode, 存储大小等</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apiVersion: v1</span><br><span class="line">kind: PersistentVolumeClaim</span><br><span class="line">metadata:</span><br><span class="line">  name: ebs-claim</span><br><span class="line">spec:</span><br><span class="line">  accessModes:</span><br><span class="line">    - ReadWriteOnce</span><br><span class="line">  storageClassName: ebs-sc</span><br><span class="line">  resources:</span><br><span class="line">    requests:</span><br><span class="line">      storage: 4Gi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>PV -  Persistent Volume 依据PVC 已经建立成功的实际PV<br>可以看到实际的vol-ID<br><img src="https://webnote.s3.cn-northwest-1.amazonaws.com.cn/20210204-pv.png" alt="pv"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;在进行操作前依据以下文档安装EBS CSI driver&lt;br&gt;依照中文版说明安装&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.aws.amazon.com/zh_cn/eks/latest/userguide/ebs-csi.html&quot;&gt;EBS CSI driver</summary>
      
    
    
    
